---
title: Paella-Style Double Garlic Prawn Risotto with Capsicum & Parsley
description: Tonight, let’s put a spin on a Spanish classic. This paella-inspired rice dish is packed with tomato and garlic goodness, and is topped with perfectly cooked prawns for a fresh hit of protein. Sprinkle over some parsley and you’ve got a dish fit for the Mediterranean!

